name: Fischl
quote: You are as I am, a traveler from another world.
description: A mysterious girl who calls herself 'Prinzessin der Verurteilung' and travels with a night raven named Oz. Through her unique abilities, eccentric character, and (while she would never admit it herself) hard work, Fischl has become a rising star among the Adventurers' Guild's investigators, earning the recognition of all.
